<br>
On the other hand, don't condemn it if you haven't tried it.  There are no abuses of chat channels there, although they do have them in limited capacity.  There is minimal twinking even allowed by the game.  There is an incredible difference in the swing between competition and cooperation.  Many, many, many more people roleplay on the roleplay servers.  In guild last night a former critic of DAoC who was trying it out for her first week said &quot;ok, ok, but I can still grumble that you can't change the size of your chat box&quot;.  We showed her how.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Plain and simple - Dark Age is NOT for everybody.  Then again, 95% of the people that I know from EQ have decided to either make Dark Age their primary or only game after a week or so of getting used to the differences.  If you don't like it, that's great too.  No one said you had to.  But being condemning it without giving it a chance is pretty toddler-ish to me. &quot;No, I won't eat my vegetables!&quot;  If you try it and hate it, then kudos to you!  (you know, those little desert bars... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )<br>
<br>
Seriously, I would think this belongs in the OT/OOC forum.  There certainly doesn't need to be a DAoC forum, though.  I would love to answer any questions folks might have about the game.  janti_eorl@yahoo.com  The RP server rules are being ENFORCED, but you can't condemn a lack of enforcement on this server simply because Verant didn't have the peanuts to actually make it a Roleplay Server.  <br>
<br>
&quot;Hey guys, ya know, we can appease these whiney roleplayers (after two years) by finally givin' them a server with the roleplay name on it, but if we put PREFERRED at th' end, we don't actually have to do schnitzel about it if peoples don' roleplay, hehe... pass the cheetos&quot;  I still love the atmosphere of this server more than any other, and for more reasons than I am allowed to go into here, but you have to admit Verant did a half arse job of it.  Oh well, it's all we have.<br>
<br>
Except for those of us that are also giving Dark Age a chance, that is.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
